{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2383,"text":"Liu Bolin: By making myself invisible,"},{"time":6278,"text":"I try to question the inter-canceling relationship"},{"time":9223,"text":"between our civilization and its development."},{"time":13102,"text":"Interpreter: By making myself invisible, I try to explore and question"},{"time":15278,"text":"the contradictory and often inter-canceling relationship"},{"time":19270,"text":"between our civilization and its development."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24622,"text":"LB: This is my first work, created in November 2005."},{"time":29828,"text":"And this is Beijing International Art Camp where I worked"},{"time":32965,"text":"before the government forcibly demolished it.I used this work to express my objection."},{"time":36500,"text":"I also want to use this work to let more people"},{"time":41689,"text":"pay attention to the living condition of artists and the condition of their creative freedom."},{"time":44029,"text":"In the meantime, from the beginning, this series has a"},{"time":46717,"text":"protesting, reflective"},{"time":51341,"text":"and uncompromising spirit."},{"time":53161,"text":"When applying makeup, I borrow a sniper's method"},{"time":57809,"text":"to better protect myself"},{"time":60165,"text":"and to detect the enemy, as he did. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64089,"text":"After finishing this series of protests,"},{"time":68557,"text":"I started questioning why my fate was like this,"},{"time":72637,"text":"and I realized that it's not just me --"},{"time":75371,"text":"all Chinese are as confused as I am."},{"time":79199,"text":"As you can see, these works"},{"time":81925,"text":"are about family planning, election in accordance with the law"},{"time":88290,"text":"and propaganda of the institution of the People's Congress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92573,"text":"This work is called Xia Gang (\"leaving post\")."},{"time":94821,"text":"\"Xia Gang\" is a Chinese euphemism for \"laid off\"."},{"time":98246,"text":"It refers to those people who lost their jobs during China's transition from a planned economy to a market economy."},{"time":105813,"text":"From 1998 to 2000,"},{"time":107685,"text":"21.37 million people"},{"time":110941,"text":"lost their jobs in China."},{"time":113718,"text":"The six people in the photo"},{"time":116642,"text":"are Xia Gang workers."},{"time":118565,"text":"I made them invisible in the deserted shop wherethey had lived and worked all their lives."},{"time":123423,"text":"On the wall behind them is the slogan of the Cultural Revolution:"},{"time":125589,"text":"\"The core force leading our cause forward is the Chinese Communist Party.\""},{"time":129750,"text":"For half a month"},{"time":131413,"text":"I looked for these 6 people to participate in my work."},{"time":133725,"text":"We can only see six men in this picture,but in fact, those who are hidden here"},{"time":138637,"text":"are all people who were laid off. They have just been made invisible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143998,"text":"This piece is called The Studio."},{"time":146142,"text":"This spring,"},{"time":147397,"text":"I happened to have an opportunity during my solo exhibition in Paris"},{"time":149822,"text":"to shoot a work in the news studio of France 3 --"},{"time":155084,"text":"I picked the news photos of the day."},{"time":157917,"text":"One is about the war in the Middle East,"},{"time":160229,"text":"and another one is about a public demonstration in France."},{"time":164317,"text":"I found that any culture has its irreconcilable contradictions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169061,"text":"This is a joint effort between me and French artist JR."},{"time":172056,"text":"Interpreter: This is a joint effort between me and French artist JR."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177185,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181038,"text":"LB: I tried to disappear into JR's eye,"},{"time":184029,"text":"but the problem is JR only uses models with big eyes."},{"time":188079,"text":"So I tried to make my eyes bigger with my fingers."},{"time":191710,"text":"But still they are not big enough for JR, unfortunately."},{"time":193144,"text":"Interpreter: So I tried to disappear into JR's eye,"},{"time":196713,"text":"but the problem is JR uses only models with big eyes."},{"time":199837,"text":"So I tried to make my eyes bigger with this gesture."},{"time":202790,"text":"But it doesn't work, my eyes are still small."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207601,"text":"LB: This one is about 9/11 memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215275,"text":"This is an aircraft carrier moored alongside the Hudson River."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220613,"text":"Kenny Scharf's graffiti."},{"time":224685,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228717,"text":"This is Venice, Italy."},{"time":232944,"text":"Because global temperatures rise,"},{"time":234945,"text":"the sea level rises, and it is said thatVenice will disappear in the coming decades."},{"time":243989,"text":"This is the ancient city of Pompeii."},{"time":246568,"text":"Interpreter: This is the ancient city of Pompeii."},{"time":257645,"text":"LB: This is the Borghese Gallery"},{"time":259383,"text":"in Rome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262784,"text":"When I work on a new piece, I pay more attention to the expression of ideas."},{"time":267069,"text":"For instance, why would I make myself invisible?"},{"time":269805,"text":"What will making myself invisible here cause people to think?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291645,"text":"This one is called Instant Noodles."},{"time":293941,"text":"Interpreter: This one is called Instant Noodles. (Laughter)"},{"time":298491,"text":"LB: Since August 2012,"},{"time":302533,"text":"harmful phosphors have been found"},{"time":307344,"text":"in the instant noodle package cups from every famous brand sold in China's supermarkets."},{"time":309603,"text":"These phosphors can even cause cancer."},{"time":312155,"text":"To create this artwork,"},{"time":314012,"text":"I bought a lot of packaged instant noodle cups"},{"time":316100,"text":"and put them in my studio, making it look like a supermarket."},{"time":319033,"text":"And my task is to stand there, trying to be still,"},{"time":321981,"text":"setting up the camera position and coordinating with my assistant"},{"time":326437,"text":"and drawing the colors and shapes that are behind my body"},{"time":329645,"text":"on the front of my body. If the background is simple,"},{"time":333790,"text":"I usually have to stand for three to four hours."},{"time":336294,"text":"The background of this piece is more complex,"},{"time":338911,"text":"so I need three to four days in advance for preparation."},{"time":343489,"text":"This is the suit I wore when I did the supermarket shoot."},{"time":346629,"text":"There is no Photoshop involved."},{"time":348907,"text":"Interpreter: This is the suit I [was] wearing when I did the supermarket shoot."},{"time":354134,"text":"There is no Photoshop involved. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360141,"text":"LB: These works are on China's cultural memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372989,"text":"And this one,"},{"time":374327,"text":"this is about food safety in China."},{"time":376989,"text":"Unsafe food can harm people's health,"},{"time":382845,"text":"and a deluge of magazines can confuse people's minds. (Laughter)"},{"time":386853,"text":"The next pieces of work show how I made myself invisible in magazines of different languages,"},{"time":389589,"text":"in different countries and at different times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394374,"text":"I think that in art, an artist's attitude is the most important element."},{"time":399243,"text":"If an artwork is to touch someone,"},{"time":403365,"text":"it must be the result of not only technique, but also the artist's thinking and struggle in life."},{"time":407029,"text":"And the repeated struggles in life create artwork,"},{"time":411405,"text":"no matter in what form."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417029,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438509,"text":"That's all I want to say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439757,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}